From: ndrewh <ndrewh@users.noreply.github.com>
Date: Sun, 22 May 2022 16:37:22 -0400
Subject: [PATCH] SRL is 'shift right logical'

Ref: https://docs.xilinx.com/v/u/2015.3-English/ug984-vivado-microblaze-ref (pg. 262)

I used this plugin to help solve the Hack-a-Sat microblaze challenges ("Blazin' Etudes" and "Ominous Etude")
---
 microblaze.py | 2 +-
 1 file changed, 1 insertion(+), 1 deletion(-)

diff --git a/microblaze.py b/microblaze.py
index e2b45e3..1873b4b 100644
--- a/microblaze.py
+++ b/microblaze.py
@@ -486,7 +486,7 @@ def lift(self, il):
         else:
             one = il.const(1, 1)
             if self.op == 'SRL':
-                val = il.shift_left(4, a, one, flags='carry')
+                val = il.logical_shift_right(4, a, one, flags='carry')
             elif self.op == 'SRA':
                 val = il.arith_shift_right(4, a, one, flags='carry')
             elif self.op == 'SRC':